xxl.core.binarySearchTrees

Class PrioritySearchTree<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • xxl.core.binarySearchTrees.PrioritySearchTree<T>

  • public class PrioritySearchTree<T>
extends Object
    A simple static Priority Serach Tree. - all event point have to be known on construction time of the tree. - no event point may occur twice as right border of an interval in the tree.

      • query

        public ArrayList<Interval1D> query(T xMax,
                                   Interval1D yRange)
        Finds all intervals [x,y] for which y lies in the interval yRange and x is less than xMax.
        Parameters:
        xMax - the upper bound for x values (not inclusive)
        yRange - the range for y values (inclusive)
        Returns:
        all intervals [x,y] with x < xMax and y in yRange
